Comment: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对女孩子来说 洗白白是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 灰大人
